Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/torment">Torment</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/torment">Torment</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user torments and enrages the foe, making it incapable of using the same move twice in a row.</p>